In [109]:
mindist = 999999
min_params = ()
maxdist = 0
max_params = ()

for i in range(1000):
    idx, ctrs, iter_ctrs = kmeans(X,2)
    dist = np.linalg.norm(X - ctrs[idx])
    if dist<mindist:
        mindist,min_params = dist,(idx, ctrs, iter_ctrs)
    if dist>maxdist:
        maxdist,max_params = dist,(idx, ctrs, iter_ctrs)
        
kmeans_plot(X, *min_params)
kmeans_plot(X, *max_params)
